        public static int[] fillTicket(int size,
                               int min,
                               int max,
                               java.lang.String errrorMessageNonNumeric,
                               java.lang.String errorMessageNonMinAndMax,
                               java.lang.String giveUniqueNumberMessage)
        This method fills a lotto ticket
        Parameters:
        size - the amount of numbers that go on the lotto ticket
        min - the smallest number that the user can choose
        max - the largest number that the user can choose
        errrorMessageNonNumeric - the error message that is displayed if the user inputs something that is not a number
        errorMessageNonMinAndMax - the error message that is displayed if the user inputs a number that is either too big or too small
        giveUniqueNumberMessage - the message to user that asks them to input a number between min and max
        Returns:
        a filled out ticket
